Binji bụ asụsụ Bantu nke ọwụwa anyanwụ Democratic Republic of the Congo
Maho (2009) na-ekwu ná ọ dị nso ná Songe, nkè dịpụrụ adịpụ n'ime asụsụ Luban nkè Ahmed guzobere (1995).
N'akwụkwọ, á na-agbagwoju yá ányá ná Mbagani, nkè na-aga otú áhà ahụ
Dịka ọmụmaatụ, Guthrie nyere koodu L.22 "Binji" màkà ihe Maho kpọrọ Mbagani; ná Maho, ezigbo Binji bụ L.231
Asụsụ abụọ ahụ kewara site na kilomita 200.
